    "architecture": "flowchart TB\n  subgraph Browser[\"Browser :3000\"]\n    UI[Next.js UI]\n    Z[Zustand localStorage]\n  end\n  subgraph BFF[\"Next.js BFF\"]\n    Proxy[\"/api/backend/*\"]\n    GenRoute[\"/api/concepts/generate\"]\n    PresRoute[\"/api/presentations/*\"]\n  end\n  subgraph API[\"NestJS :3001\"]\n    C[Controllers]\n    GS[GenerationService]\n    AS[AgentRunService]\n    GQ[(queue: generation)]\n    AQ[(queue: agent-run)]\n  end\n  subgraph AI[\"OpenRouter\"]\n    LLM[LLM chat]\n    IMG[Image gen Gemini/Flux]\n  end\n  UI --> Proxy\n  UI --> GenRoute\n  UI --> PresRoute\n  Proxy --> C\n  GenRoute --> C\n  PresRoute --> LLM\n  C --> GS --> GQ\n  C --> AS --> AQ\n  GQ --> IMG\n  AQ --> LLM\n  AQ --> IMG\n  Z --> UI",
    "creativeAgent": "flowchart LR\n  A[POST agent-run creative] --> B[AgentRunProcessor]\n  B --> C[IdeatorAgent]\n  C --> D[CriticAgent top 5]\n  D --> E{CREATIVE_FLUX_PREVIEW?}\n  E -->|да| F[Flux Klein preview x5]\n  E -->|нет| G[awaiting_idea_selection]\n  F --> G\n  G --> H[User picks]\n  H --> I[PromptBuilderAgent]\n  I --> J[OpenRouter Gemini final]",
    "catalogAgent": "flowchart LR\n  A[POST agent-run catalog] --> B[prepareCatalogPipeline]\n  B --> C[SQL prefilter + stratified shortlist max 200]\n  C --> D[CatalogIdeator gpt-4o-mini:floor]\n  D --> E[CatalogBuyer нейро-байер: SKU по слотам gpt-4o-mini:floor]\n  E --> F[CatalogLlmSetCritic gemini-2.5-flash-lite]\n  F --> G[set-assembler 5 concepts parallel]\n  G --> H[awaiting_idea_selection]",
    "generationWorker": "flowchart TD\n  J[BullMQ generate] --> P[GenerationProcessor]\n  P --> L{LLM phase}\n  L -->|creative+agents| PB[ConceptPromptService]\n  L -->|else| LB[LlmBriefService]\n  PB --> IP[Build image prompt]\n  LB --> IP\n  IP --> OR[OpenRouter Image PRIMARY]\n  OR -->|fail| FB[HF FLUX / Pollinations / Horde]\n  OR --> CR[mergeConceptResult]\n  FB --> CR\n  CR --> DB[(PostgreSQL)]"
  },
